      "html": "<h2 align=\"center\" style=\"color: #2c3e50;\">Code Example</h2><div style=\"background: #282c34; color: #abb2bf; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; margin: 1rem 0; overflow-x: auto;\"><pre style=\"margin: 0;\"><span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">async function</span> <span style=\"color: #61dafb;\">processOrder</span>(<span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">orderData</span>) {\n  <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">try</span> {\n    <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">const</span> <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">validation</span> = <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">await</span> <span style=\"color: #61dafb;\">validateOrder</span>(<span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">orderData</span>);\n    <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">const</span> <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">payment</span> = <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">await</span> <span style=\"color: #61dafb;\">processPayment</span>(<span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">orderData</span>);\n    <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">const</span> <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">order</span> = <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">await</span> <span style=\"color: #61dafb;\">createOrder</span>(<span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">orderData</span>, <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">payment</span>);\n    \n    <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">return</span> { <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">success</span>: <span style=\"color: #d19a66;\">true</span>, <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">orderId</span>: <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">order</span>.<span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">id</span> };\n  } <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">catch</span> (<span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">error</span>) {\n    <span style=\"color: #61dafb;\">logger</span>.<span style=\"color: #61dafb;\">error</span>(<span style=\"color: #98c379;\">'Order processing failed'</span>, <span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">error</span>);\n    <span style=\"color: #c678dd;\">throw new</span> <span style=\"color: #61dafb;\">OrderProcessingError</span>(<span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">error</span>.<span style=\"color: #e06c75;\">message</span>);\n  }\n}</pre></div><p><small><em>TypeScript implementation with proper error handling and logging</em></small></p>",
